room_title: Escape room "Gangster's Hideaway" by Speakeasy Escape Room in Virginia Beach
room_description:
The rival crew is out on a poker run, so we decided to break in and steal their loot.
Gotta' be quick, they are not going to like it if all of us jokers are still inside by the time they get back! Get in, get out, DON'T get caught!
